g.desc: The variable skb->data_len records the length of all packages...
g.text: The variable skb->data_len records the length of all packages in frags[] and frag_list. If it is not zero, the skb is nonlinear, see skb_is_nonlinear().skb->data_len = sum(skb_shared_info->frags[i]->size) + sum(skb_shared_info->frag_list->len)
